  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "V\u1EADy La-ban \u0111u\u1ED5i k\u1ECBp Gia-c\u1ED1p. L\xFAc \u0111\xF3 Gia-c\u1ED1p \u0111ang d\u1EF1ng tr\u1EA1i trong v\xF9ng n\xFAi, c\xF2n La-ban v\xE0 gia nh\xE2n \u0111\xF3ng tr\u1EA1i trong n\xFAi Ghi-l\xEA-\xE1t. "), mdx("h6", {
