  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "La-ban h\u1ECFi Gia-c\u1ED1p, \"Ch\xE1u l\xE0m chuy\u1EC7n g\xEC v\u1EADy? Ch\xE1u g\u1EA1t c\u1EADu, mang c\xE1c con g\xE1i c\u1EADu \u0111i nh\u01B0 th\u1EC3 t\xF9 binh. "), mdx("h6", {
