    "id": "v28"
  }, "v28"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xE1u c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng cho c\u1EADu c\xF3 d\u1ECBp h\xF4n t\u1EEB gi\xE3 c\xE1c ch\xE1u v\xE0 con g\xE1i c\u1EE7a c\u1EADu n\u1EEFa. Ch\xE1u l\xE0m chuy\u1EC7n n\u1EA7y th\u1EADt qu\xE1 ngu xu\u1EA9n! "), mdx("h6", {
