  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "Ra-ch\xEAn gi\u1EA5u c\xE1c t\u01B0\u1EE3ng ch\u1EA1m b\xEAn d\u01B0\u1EDBi y\xEAn l\u1EA1c \u0111\xE0 r\u1ED3i ng\u1ED3i l\xEAn tr\xEAn. La-ban l\u1EE5c so\xE1t kh\u1EAFp l\u1EC1u nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng th\u1EA5y. "), mdx("h6", {
