  }, "v38"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xE1u \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m vi\u1EC7c cho c\u1EADu su\u1ED1t hai m\u01B0\u01A1i n\u0103m nay, trong th\u1EDDi gian \u0111\xF3 kh\xF4ng h\u1EC1 c\xF3 m\u1ED9t con chi\xEAn hay con d\xEA c\xE1i n\xE0o s\u1EA3o thai, ch\xE1u kh\xF4ng h\u1EC1 \u0103n m\u1ED9t con chi\xEAn hay d\xEA \u0111\u1EF1c n\xE0o trong b\u1EA7y c\u1EE7a c\u1EADu. "), mdx("h6", {
